    "# Website Content Creator\n",
    "- find all website link\n",
    "- Find product type from given list\n",
    "- Content and keyword must from Native location\n",
    "- Also find competitor website and find keywords which are bringing conversions\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "URL: https://www.boneinlayfurnitures.com/products/hand-carved-menagerie-buffet-black-credenza  \n",
    "\n",
    "You are a SEO expert and you have to write \"Product description\", \"SEO Meta description\" using below keywords for above product link. You can get product description idea from existing website URL. \n",
    "We want language of content should be native for USA, UK and Europe customers. Length of content should be under 160 character .  \n",
    "Must include essential keywords in content: Vintage, Antique  \n",
    "Relevant keywords: [Handmade sideboard,Vintage furniture sideboard,  \n",
    "Custom-made sideboards,Mid-century sideboard,  \n",
    "Painted Sideboard,Traditional Sideboard,Vintage sideboard]  \n",
    "Top keywords: Solid wood furniture, indian furniture, Handmade  \n",
    "\n",
    "Based on the information from the page, the top keywords are:\n",
    "\n",
    "Product keyword: Hand Carved Menagerie Buffet, Hand-carved Menagerie Sideboard, Buffet Table, Sideboard\n",
    "Style/Material keyword: Hand-carved, Handmade, Solid Wood, Black Color, Wildlife-inspired, Vintage, Antique\n",
    "\n",
    "Also provide some meta keywords and long tail keyword list for website which are trending for UK, USA and Switzerland Location. \n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "### Important \n",
    "\"\"\"\n",
    "write a code for custom LangChain tool that connects to the Google Search Console API to pull your website’s performance data, including top keywords, clicks, and impressions \n",
    "\"\"\"\n",
    "- Connect with google analytics to get the performance score and adjust the strategy accordingly\n",
    "- Use google Search Console API to identify best performing keyword and search queries which you can include in website or in blogs"
   ]
